data.description: So closes to shopping and restaurants. .  SWIMMING POOL VERY CLOSE TO HOUSE!  Upon entry, you are greeted with clay hard surface floors leading from the foyer into the kitchen with the kitchen offering stainless appliances, an abundance of storage space, and an eating space with natural lighting pouring in. New carpet has been installed in the dining room and the large greatroom. The laundry room and half bath complete this level. Upstairs, you'll find the spacious primary suite with the bathroom offering a walk in shower. Three additional large bedrooms and a full bath complete this level. Relax or entertain guests in the finished rec room on the lower levelwith new carpet and a dedicated HOME THEATER  with wall speakers.  Paver brick patio!
